# ✅ **3. PlantUML Diagram**

👉 Keep it simple but show the **3-step validation flow** (this is the only extra complexity)

```plantuml
@startuml
actor User
participant Ui
participant CcaLedger
participant Parser
participant AddResidentToEventCommand
participant ResidentManager
participant CcaManager
participant EventManager

User -> Ui: enter "add-resident-to-event A123 Hackathon ComputingClub"
Ui -> CcaLedger: input

CcaLedger -> Parser: parse(input)
Parser -> AddResidentToEventCommand: new AddResidentToEventCommand(...)

CcaLedger -> AddResidentToEventCommand: execute(...)

AddResidentToEventCommand -> ResidentManager: findResident(matricNumber)
AddResidentToEventCommand -> CcaManager: findCca(ccaName)

alt all exist
    AddResidentToEventCommand -> EventManager: addResidentToEvent(eventName, cca, resident)
    AddResidentToEventCommand -> Ui: showMessage(...)
else not found
    AddResidentToEventCommand -> Ui: showError(...)
end
@enduml